---
import Card from '../Card.astro';
---

<section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900">
        You don't need another budget. You need clarity.
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 flex justify-center">
      <Card class="text-center max-w-md">
        <div class="text-4xl mb-4">{'\u{1F61F}'}</div>
        <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">
          Every purchase comes with guilt
        </h3>
        <p class="text-slate-600">
          Without a clear number, every coffee, every dinner out carries a whisper: "should I be spending this?"
        </p>
      </Card>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-12 text-center text-lg text-slate-600 italic">
      What if there was a simpler way?
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
